Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:57.94,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.94,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}No No No don't worry 1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.11,OP-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an2\blur7}吹き返す　心臓のリズム
